    "Another problem found was in the correction mechanism of this chain.",
    "Upon generating incorrect SQL and executing it in the database, the error feedback was returned to the LLM to fix the SQL query, but it continued to generate the query incorrectly.",
    "C3 significantly enhances LLM's performance in handling simple and complex queries.",
    "Clear Prompting offers effective prompts that help the LLM to better comprehend the query intent and the database schema structure.",
    "As it captures only specific tables and columns, it increases the clarity on how joins should be synthesized."
